data.eml:eml: A new species of Uperoleia (Anura: Myobatrachidae) from the northwest Kimberley, Western Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Doughty, Paul, Roberts, Dale (2008): A new species of Uperoleia (Anura: Myobatrachidae) from the northwest Kimberley, Western Australia. Zootaxa 1939: 10-18, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.185001
